headline: Waters Corporation Schedules First Quarter 2025 Earnings Conference Call
summary: Waters Corporation (NYSE:WAT) will hold its Q1 2025 financial results conference call on Tuesday, May 6th, 2025 at 8:00 a.m. Eastern Time. A live webcast of the presentation will be available on Waters Investor Relations website at https://ir.waters.com. A replay of the webcast will also be available until at least June 3rd, 2025, at midnight Eastern Time.
